== Umugambi ==
Umuyobozi w’umutekano Harry Webb afite ubwoba ko ubujura bwa diyama bugiye kubera mu ruganda rukora ubucukuzi bw’amabuye y'agaciro mu butayu<ref>Killer Force Movie Poster - IMP Awards <nowiki>http://www.impawards.com</nowiki> › killer_force</ref>. Yahise abasha gukundwa cyane,  na Claire Chambers, umukobwa wamamaye cyane  n'umukobwa w'umuyobozi w'ibirombe<ref>Killer Force (1976) - Cast & Crew - The Movie Database <nowiki>https://www.themoviedb.org</nowiki> › movie › cast</ref>. Arimo gusura umugabo akunda, Mike Bradley, ushinzwe umutekano kuri iki kirombe<ref>Killer Force Cast Members List - FamousFix <nowiki>https://www.famousfix.com</nowiki> › topic › killer-force › cast</ref>.

Nelson, umuyobozi w’ibirombe, aha Bradley ubutumwa bw'amatsiko - kwiba diyama. Arashaka kugira uruhare kuri Bradley kugira ngo amuhuze na Lewis runaka witegura kwiba ikirombe abifashijwemo n'itsinda ry'abacanshuro ndetse n'ibikoresho byaho bizwi nka Padiri Noheri<ref>Killer Force (1975) - Val Guest | Cast and Crew | AllMovie <nowiki>https://www.allmovie.com</nowiki> › movie › killer-force-v27294</ref>. Webb, itamenyeshejwe uburiganya, idahwema gukurikirana Bradley, wavuganye na Lewis. Hamwe n'abacanshuro mugikorwa cyo kwinjira mu kirombe, Bradley yerekanye ko ari Padiri Noheri, wateguye iki gikorwa cyose. Hamwe na Webb ikurikirana, Bradley yahungiye mu butayu hamwe nabandi barokotse<ref>Movie Actors - TheTVDB.com <nowiki>https://thetvdb.com</nowiki> › movies › killer-force › people</ref>.

